{"tid":910356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瘋了瘋了]設計師IG辱「中國是屎國」！章子怡、黃曉明眾大咖抵制DG秀","createTime":"2018-11-21T06:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T15:57:23.000Z","uid":67294,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb94a2c73bf614a254ed25e0b0b887a17336f3e","tid":910356,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"義大利品牌Dolce &amp; Gabbana（簡稱DG）今晚將在上海舉辦品牌大秀，卻被曝出疑似其設計師在IG發布<strong>「中國是屎國，我們沒有你（中國）也活得很好」</strong>的辱華言論，引發爭議。目前章子怡、李冰冰、陳坤、黃曉明、王大陸、王俊凱、火箭少女101、陳學冬等藝人均已公開表態不會出席其大秀活動，部分模特兒也表態不會為其走秀。章子怡工作室更發聲明表示，章子怡及團隊不會購買和使用DG任何產品。<br />\n<strong>Dolce &amp; Gabbana品牌與設計師則宣稱IG被盜，他們喜歡中國、喜歡中國文化。</strong>（娛樂中心、薛佳甯／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181121/640_17b801a86713af9c2f381996a5878ca4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181121%2F640_17b801a86713af9c2f381996a5878ca4.jpg&h=591c5648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDolce &amp; Gabbana設計師在IG與網友對話，譏罵中國是屎國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181121/640_b7f6b2d570f2ff6300ced64e04f4ddc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181121%2F640_b7f6b2d570f2ff6300ced64e04f4ddc8.jpg&h=ffc15f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDolce &amp; Gabbana微博澄清IG被盜帳號。"},{"pid":"2adb065f44640f336723286a3a4abda997825d8f","tid":910356,"uid":51701,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"141 補習導師"},{"pid":"f59d5d7c9f8e8b019683478f8c7e8936337e49cc","tid":910356,"uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"2adb065f44640f336723286a3a4abda997825d8f","tid":910356,"uid":51701,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"141 補習導師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"1e0